last_episode_to_air.name: Tina's Wedding
last_episode_to_air.overview: Tina’s wedding day arrives along with all of her fears about marriage and the next chapter of her life.

name: Twenty
overview: A lesbian musician struggles to break her patterns of whirlwind romances while serving as the shoulder to lean on for a group of eclectic friends, who offer little in return.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Maya's going to meet old college friends who want to spice up their sex life, new love interests who might turn out to be the love of her life, an ex-girlfriend who's still occupying her mind, and lot's of awkward blind dates. All while she's serving as the shoulder to lean on for her eclectic friends, who offer little in return and drag her into their own shenanigans.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Follows the story of Maya, her girlfriend Catalina, and her group of eclectic friends as they navigate careers, love, and life in their early twenties.

episodes.name: Threesome
episodes.overview: Maya invites her college friends and couple Victoria and Charles over to her place for an evening full of surprises and misunderstandings.

episodes.name: Dad's New Girlfriend
episodes.overview: After Maya meets with her childhood friend Tina at the beach, she's invited to eat lunch with her dad and his new girlfriend.

episodes.name: Girls Night Out
episodes.overview: While Tina isn't in the club they wanted to meet later, and getting in the middle of Charles and Victoria's breakup, Maya meets someone special.

episodes.name: Palmdale
episodes.overview: After a one night stand with some stranger, Maya has to pick up Tina in the middle of the desert.

episodes.name: The First Date
episodes.overview: For her first date with Catalina, Maya tries to make a perfect paella and speak to her convincingly in Spanish - which turns out pretty well ...

episodes.name: Plan B
episodes.overview: While Maya is falling head over heals for Catalina, Tina reveals that she might be pregnant.

episodes.name: Peru
episodes.overview: After asking her to be her girlfriend, Catalina has to tell something important to Maya.

episodes.name: Love Is Blind
episodes.overview: Set up by Hazel and Tina, Maya has to go on a series of awkward blind dates.

episodes.name: Liz
episodes.overview: Maya's ex-girlfriend Liz is back in town on a business trip and ends up having dinner with her, Victoria, and Victoria's new lover.

episodes.name: The Night Owl
episodes.overview: After Tina invited her to dinner to meet her newly found love of her life, Maya meets writer Sophie outside, who helps her with the parking meter.

episodes.name: The Mongolian Fish
episodes.overview: As planned, Maya and Sophie meet Tina for the awkward dinner, surprised about the identity of her new lover, the Night Owl.

episodes.name: Ohm My God
episodes.overview: Maya and Tina attend an awkward yoga class. Later, she meets with Sophie, and her dad calls to tell her some important news.

episodes.name: Vancouver
episodes.overview: When Sophie asks Maya to move with her to Vancouver, she has to take some time to think about it. Meanwhile, Hazel meets Iris, Victoria and Charles joined a cult, and Tina and Hector are engaged. But neither of that is the biggest surprise for Maya ...

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: Maya's going to meet old college friends who want to spice up their sex life, new love interests who might turn out to be the love of her life, an ex-girlfriend who's still occupying her mind, and lot's of awkward blind dates. All while she's serving as the shoulder to lean on for her eclectic friends, who offer little in return and drag her into their own shenanigans.

episodes.name: The Party: Part 1
episodes.overview: Tina enlists Maya's help to ask Victoria to be one of her bridesmaid's. Catalina and Maya go to Hazel's birthday party where they run into an unexpected guest.

episodes.name: The Party: Part 2
episodes.overview: Victoria shows up at Hazel's party with a message for Tina. Catalina and Maya get some unexpected news.

episodes.name: Beards From High School
episodes.overview: Maya rehearses in anticipation for her show with Valerie. Tina and Maya go to test out hairstyles for the wedding when they run into Rajiv, Maya's beard from high school, who has some shocking news.

episodes.name: Cheesy Fries
episodes.overview: Maya and Catalina visit Christopher and Carson at their new beach house. Hazel and Iris get into a fight at the fast food drive in.

episodes.name: Valerie
episodes.overview: Maya talks with Hazel about her breakup with Iris, before going to meet Valerie to prepare for the concert. Maya inherits an unexpected house guest.

episodes.name: Tina's Visit
episodes.overview: Living with Tina turns out to be more difficult than Maya and Catalina anticipated. The trio run into Victoria and her surprising new love interest on a hike.

episodes.name: Valentine's Day
episodes.overview: Maya goes to rehearse with Valerie and enlists the help of Tina to pull off her Valentine's Day plans.

episodes.name: Showtime
episodes.overview: It's showtime for Valerie and Maya. At the concert Catalina surprises Maya with some unexpected information about her past.

episodes.name: The Bachelorette Weekend: Part 1
episodes.overview: Ever wonder what Tina's bachelorette party might look like?

episodes.name: The Bachelorette Weekend: Part 2
episodes.overview: Maya, Tina, Liz and Hazel find themselves in a sticky situation with a shady desert rat after getting drinks at a local bar.

episodes.name: The Bachelorette Weekend: Part 3
episodes.overview: In another bar, several drinks later, Maya meets someone from the past - and the bachelorette weekend is still not over.

episodes.name: The Bachelorette Weekend: Part 4
episodes.overview: After an unfortunate encounter with a police officer, Maya, Tina, Hazel and Liz end up in jail and can only think of one person to bail them out. Except, Maya doesn't want to call her.

episodes.name: Tina's Wedding
episodes.overview: Tina’s wedding day arrives along with all of her fears about marriage and the next chapter of her life.
